Vulois ran down into the main chamber. He saw Child standing in the 
entrance of one of the other tunnels. He went over to him.

"What are you doing? You should've stayed at the camp. And if you had 
gone down this tunnel you would've been lost forever! What do 
you...what the?"

Vulois looked the picture of the angel up and down.

"By the Matrix.......What do you think it is?"

Gotron


Gotron followed the rest of the alliance membres going after the ship.
_____________________________________________________________________
Zava


Zava watched as the dump engines clock ticked down to 2:30, but the 
explosion clock ticked down to 0:30.

"Hahahaha! 30 seconds until the Maximals die! Now, for Deemos, I give 
m life! I don't want to die in this hideous explosion."

Zava stepped away from the engines, and put her blaster to her head.

"For Deemos......"

Zava pulled the trigger, and mech fluid spat everywhere. She crumpled 
to the ground. So ends the life of Zava of the Chosen ones, another 
lost soul sucked in by Deemos' magic. Yet still her wrath continues, 
as the clock on the engines ticks down.

0:29.....0:28.....

(All of my female charcters die basically as soon as I have them, and 
bymy accord. Why do I do this? I don't hate women.)
